whenever I mentioned Qingchen.

34
00:01:45,565 --> 00:01:47,364
She's probably jealous.

35
00:01:47,365 --> 00:01:50,085
Gosh, she must be imagining things.

36
00:01:50,325 --> 00:01:51,515
Do you really

37
