84
00:05:31,005 --> 00:05:32,365
Chen Qingqing.

85
00:05:52,445 --> 00:05:53,625
Chen Qingqing.

86
00:05:53,965 --> 00:05:56,315
Qingqing, are you still alive?

87
00:05:58,445 --> 00:05:59,285
Qingqing.

88
00:06:03,565 --> 00:06:05,405
It's me, Situ Feng.

89
00:06:06,045 --> 00:06:07,325
Situ Feng.

90
00:06:07,605 --> 00:06:09,284
Do you find pleasure in dressing up?

91
00:06:09,285 --> 00:06:10,535
Are you crazy?

92
00:06:11,525 --> 00:06:13,765
Yes, I'm crazy.

93
00:06:14,645 --> 00:06:19,615
