96
00:06:26,645 --> 00:06:27,725
This...

97
00:06:27,845 --> 00:06:30,444
When I was sleeping,
I accidentally bumped my head.

98
00:06:30,445 --> 00:06:32,044
It's not a big deal.

99
00:06:32,045 --> 00:06:34,035
