133
00:08:26,645 --> 00:08:28,635
I was always home alone.

134
00:08:28,725 --> 00:08:31,095
That's when I began to cook.

135
00:08:31,405 --> 00:08:33,155
That's good for you.

136
00:08:33,725 --> 00:08:35,525
By the way, Qingqing--

137
00:08:38,645 --> 00:08:40,045
Pervert!

138
00:08:41,485 --> 00:08:43,364
-Fangfang!
-Don't you worry, Qingqing.

139
00:08:43,365 --> 00:08:44,884
-I will catch him for you!
-Wait!

140
00:08:44,885 --> 00:08:46,085
Fangfang!

141
00:08:47,845 --> 00:08:49,164
Stop running, you pervert!

142
00:08:49,165 --> 00:08:51,324
We need to catch this pervert!

143
00:08:51,325 --> 00:08:53,015
Let's hit him hard!

144
00:09:02,565 --> 00:09:05,585
-Stop right there!
-Catch that pervert!

145
00:09:08,285 --> 00:09:09,485
