146
00:09:10,245 --> 00:09:12,475
Are you all right, Qingqing?

147
00:09:13,645 --> 00:09:15,815
I'm fine, thanks, Fangfang.

148
00:09:20,165 --> 00:09:21,284
-Fangfang!
-Hey, Fangfang.

149
00:09:21,285 --> 00:09:23,685
