153
00:09:29,845 --> 00:09:31,204
Yes, what did he look like?

154
00:09:31,205 --> 00:09:34,684
He was wearing a dress,
but his hair was short like a guy.

155
00:09:34,685 --> 00:09:36,244
I couldn't really see his face.

156
00:09:36,245 --> 00:09:38,204
-What a weirdo.
-Goodness.

157
00:09:38,205 --> 00:09:39,644
Luckily, I went back in time.

158
00:09:39,645 --> 00:09:41,444
He wasn't able to do anything to Qingqing.

159
00:09:41,445 --> 00:09:44,805
-Great job, Fangfang.
-Great job.

160
00:09:45,325 --> 00:09:46,525
Situ Feng.

161
00:09:47,085 --> 00:09:50,884
Do you have any idea about the pervert
they were talking about?

162
00:09:50,885 --> 00:09:51,725
Me?

163
00:09:51,845 --> 00:09:54,165
How would I know?

164
00:09:54,245 --> 00:09:57,215
I'm glad nothing happened to Qingqing.

165
00:09:58,045 --> 00:09:59,004
That's odd.

166
00:09:59,005 --> 00:10:01,684
Shouldn't you be worried
about Chen Qingqing?

167
00:10:01,685 --> 00:10:02,525
I am.

168
00:10:02,925 --> 00:10:05,204
I'm worried. I am really worried.

169
00:10:05,205 --> 00:10:06,145
All right.

170
00:10:25,925 --> 00:10:26,765
Hey.

171
00:10:27,365 --> 00:10:29,785
You're finally here for class.

172
00:10:31,805 --> 00:10:32,685
