173
00:10:34,365 --> 00:10:36,804
Qingqing, were you all right yesterday

174
00:10:36,805 --> 00:10:39,645
after being harassed by that pervert?

175
00:10:43,725 --> 00:10:44,675
I'm fine.

176
00:10:45,645 --> 00:10:47,085
That's a relief.

177
00:10:52,205 --> 00:10:53,244
-Qingqing.
-Yes?

178
00:10:53,245 --> 00:10:56,524
