while they were eloping.

189
00:11:46,165 --> 00:11:47,105
I think...

190
00:11:47,165 --> 00:11:48,644
INFLUENTIAL FAMILY IN JINCHENG

191
00:11:48,645 --> 00:11:53,775
I think the news was going to affect
Ming De College's reputation.

192
00:11:54,045 --> 00:11:57,525
