193
00:11:58,925 --> 00:12:00,085
But...

194
00:12:01,685 --> 00:12:03,735
But my grandpa told me...

195
00:12:07,285 --> 00:12:08,285
Qingqing.

196
00:12:08,925 --> 00:12:11,444
Perhaps your grandpa kept this a secret

197
00:12:11,445 --> 00:12:13,005
for your own good.

198
00:12:17,965 --> 00:12:19,645
Thank you, Ms. Chen.

199
00:12:31,845 --> 00:12:33,445
Hello, Qingqing.

200
00:12:33,965 --> 00:12:34,845
Grandpa.

201
00:12:36,405 --> 00:12:40,175
My parents passed away
in a car accident, right?

202
00:12:41,325 --> 00:12:44,005
My mom didn't die of an illness.

203
00:12:44,845 --> 00:12:47,444
My dad didn't leave to enjoy his life.

204
00:12:47,445 --> 00:12:50,324
They were being pushed to the edge by you.

205
00:12:50,325 --> 00:12:53,724
That's how they got
into an accident, am I right?

206
00:12:53,725 --> 00:12:54,565
Qingqing.

207
00:12:55,525 --> 00:12:58,204
I was only doing this for your own good.

208
00:12:58,205 --> 00:13:00,765
So it was all a lie.

209
00:13:01,405 --> 00:13:02,325
Liar!

210
00:13:04,205 --> 00:13:06,764
I don't want to listen to you anymore.

211
00:13:06,765 --> 00:13:09,325
I don't want to listen to you.

212
00:13:20,405 --> 00:13:21,924
That is Mr. Xiao Jingnan.

213
00:13:21,925 --> 00:13:23,524
He's an honorary alumnus of our school.

214
00:13:23,525 --> 00:13:25,804
He used to be
the president of the School Council

215
00:13:25,805 --> 00:13:27,884
and has made great contributions
to the school.

216
00:13:27,885 --> 00:13:29,445
XIAO JINGNAN

217
00:13:30,445 --> 00:13:32,325
CHEN YOUYOU

218
00:13:38,965 --> 00:13:41,365
Your mom was like a hero.

219
00:13:41,445 --> 00:13:43,444
Ever since I got to know her,

220
00:13:43,445 --> 00:13:46,485
