221
00:13:46,685 --> 00:13:48,365
This photo was taken

222
00:13:48,405 --> 00:13:50,635
when your parents first met.

223
00:13:50,645 --> 00:13:52,444
Two people who really love each other

224
00:13:52,445 --> 00:13:54,204
will surely outdo themselves

225
00:13:54,205 --> 00:13:55,845
for one another.

226
00:13:55,925 --> 00:13:57,005
Qingqing.

227
00:13:57,565 --> 00:13:59,284
We wanted to tell you

228
00:13:59,285 --> 00:14:01,764
that you're a smart and beautiful girl.

229
00:14:01,765 --> 00:14:03,515
We are proud of you.

230
00:14:04,405 --> 00:14:07,575
But more than that, we hope you will be

231
00:14:07,805 --> 00:14:09,965
a happy and brave girl

232
00:14:10,045 --> 00:14:12,595
and go after the life you want.

233
00:14:57,045 --> 00:14:58,545
She's over there.

234
00:15:01,005 --> 00:15:02,644
-Qingqing.
-Qingqing.

235
00:15:02,645 --> 00:15:04,675
-Qingqing.
-What happened?

236
00:15:04,885 --> 00:15:06,325
What's going on?

237
00:15:09,325 --> 00:15:12,555
I'm afraid I have to leave this college.

238
00:15:14,885 --> 00:15:15,925
My dad...

239
00:15:17,325 --> 00:15:18,945
He has passed away.

240
00:15:27,685 --> 00:15:29,005
I was hopeful

241
00:15:30,565 --> 00:15:33,295
when I first came to this college.

242
00:15:33,565 --> 00:15:36,985
I thought this is how I could find my dad.

243
00:15:39,605 --> 00:15:40,445
But...

244
00:15:43,165 --> 00:15:45,045
After hearing the news,

245
00:15:46,725 --> 00:15:48,845
I don't see hope anymore.

246
00:15:50,365 --> 00:15:52,215
Everything is shattered.

247
00:15:55,765 --> 00:15:57,205
Should I stay?

248
00:15:59,365 --> 00:16:00,625
I'm not sure.

249
00:16:02,445 --> 00:16:04,045
I feel like

250
00:16:06,445 --> 00:16:08,005
everything has lost

251
00:16:09,245 --> 00:16:11,045
its meaning.

252
00:16:12,645 --> 00:16:13,604
That's not true.

253
00:16:13,605 --> 00:16:14,445
Qingqing.

254
00:16:15,405 --> 00:16:16,884
You still have us.

255
00:16:16,885 --> 00:16:18,815
We're all your friends.

256
00:16:20,045 --> 00:16:24,135
You still have a reason to stay
at Ming De College.

257
00:16:25,525 --> 00:16:26,955
You must remember

258
00:16:27,445 --> 00:16:29,435
that you're never alone.

259
00:16:32,205 --> 00:16:33,085
Qingqing.

260
00:16:36,485 --> 00:16:37,485
Don't go.

261
00:16:51,125 --> 00:16:52,244
Chen Qingqing.

262
00:16:52,245 --> 00:16:54,404
Was I not clear about this?

263
00:16:54,405 --> 00:16:58,604
It has been a long day.
Is that all that you've done?

264
00:16:58,605 --> 00:17:00,535
What's going on, Xinya?

265
00:17:01,285 --> 00:17:02,165
Mr. Gu.

266
00:17:02,765 --> 00:17:04,244
It's good that you're here.

267
00:17:04,245 --> 00:17:06,284
I told her to organize
the files for the freshmen.

268
00:17:06,285 --> 00:17:08,724
She mixed up all the files
for the sophomores and the juniors.

269
00:17:08,725 --> 00:17:10,924
Even the order of arrangements
were all wrong.

270
00:17:10,925 --> 00:17:12,185
I don't care.

271
00:17:12,365 --> 00:17:15,044
You have to complete
all these files today.

272
00:17:15,045 --> 00:17:15,925
Okay.

273
00:17:16,565 --> 00:17:19,004
I will bring them home with me
to finish them

274
00:17:19,005 --> 00:17:21,084
and submit them to you by tomorrow.

275
00:17:21,085 --> 00:17:22,804
Remember your promise.

276
00:17:22,805 --> 00:17:23,995
Don't forget.

277
00:17:32,685 --> 00:17:34,795
Qingqing, let me help you.

278
00:17:38,045 --> 00:17:38,885
Thanks.

279
00:17:40,245 --> 00:17:42,795
I will help you with the files.

280
00:17:43,045 --> 00:17:45,345
You should go back and rest.

281
00:17:45,605 --> 00:17:47,165
Leave these to me.

282
00:17:47,645 --> 00:17:49,155
I can't do that.

283
00:17:50,205 --> 00:17:52,245
This is my responsibility.

284
00:17:52,845 --> 00:17:54,684
Don't be so hard on yourself.

285
00:17:54,685 --> 00:17:56,604
Given your current state,

286
00:17:56,605 --> 00:18:00,375
it might take forever
to finish all these files.

287
00:18:01,045 --> 00:18:02,085
Qingqing.

288
00:18:02,805 --> 00:18:07,445
Do you still remember what I told you
back at the campsite?

289
00:18:07,445 --> 00:18:09,084
If you ever need help,

290
00:18:09,085 --> 00:18:10,484
you should come look and for me.

291
00:18:10,485 --> 00:18:12,595
Never keep it to yourself.

292
00:18:17,845 --> 00:18:19,345
Go back and rest.

293
00:18:19,525 --> 00:18:21,364
I'm heading over to the office now.

294
00:18:21,365 --> 00:18:22,365
Okay.

295
00:18:23,725 --> 00:18:25,285
Thank you so much.

296
00:18:25,485 --> 00:18:26,985
Don't mention it.

297
00:18:42,805 --> 00:18:46,385
CHEN QINGQING, DATE OF BIRTH,
JANUARY 30, 1999

298
00:18:55,845 --> 00:18:56,685
Fangfang.

299
00:18:57,805 --> 00:18:59,985
Why did you bring me here?

300
00:19:00,645 --> 00:19:03,804
You've been staying in campus
most of the time.

301
00:19:03,805 --> 00:19:05,684
We should get out sometime.

302
00:19:05,685 --> 00:19:06,885
Get out?

303
00:19:09,045 --> 00:19:10,925
But it's so dark here

304
00:19:11,965 --> 00:19:14,205
and there's nothing to see.

305
00:19:17,525 --> 00:19:18,405
Fangfang.

306
00:19:21,165 --> 00:19:22,005
Fangfang.

307
00:19:25,285 --> 00:19:26,245
Fangfang!

308
00:19:28,725 --> 00:19:29,725
Fangfang.

309
00:19:51,725 --> 00:19:53,844
-Happy Birthday, Qingqing!
-Happy Birthday!

310
00:19:53,845 --> 00:19:54,924
Thank you, guys.

311
00:19:54,925 --> 00:19:57,364
How did you know today was my birthday?

312
00:19:57,365 --> 00:20:00,205
Baby, you should thank our president.

313
00:20:00,285 --> 00:20:04,244
I was organizing some files
and I accidentally saw yours.

314
00:20:04,245 --> 00:20:06,724
So I thought of gathering everyone
to celebrate your birthday.

315
00:20:06,725 --> 00:20:07,724
I hope you don't mind.

316
00:20:07,725 --> 00:20:09,085
Of course not!

317
00:20:09,165 --> 00:20:11,005
Thank you, Gu Nanxi.

318
00:20:13,085 --> 00:20:15,765
Did you put up all these lights?

319
00:20:15,845 --> 00:20:16,885
Yes.

320
00:20:16,965 --> 00:20:18,575
They look beautiful.

321
00:20:20,605 --> 00:20:21,445
Qingqing.

322
00:20:22,085 --> 00:20:23,215
Make a wish.

323
00:20:24,325 --> 00:20:26,284
Congratulations, baby.
You're one year older.

324
00:20:26,285 --> 00:20:27,655
You're annoying!

325
00:20:28,165 --> 00:20:29,284
Don't mind him.

326
00:20:29,285 --> 00:20:31,364
You will always be 18 years old to us.

327
00:20:31,365 --> 00:20:33,235
Hurry up, make a wish.

328
00:20:47,325 --> 00:20:49,244
All right, let's have some cake!

329
00:20:49,245 --> 00:20:52,005
-Great!
-Wow!

330
00:21:46,525 --> 00:21:47,965
It has gone out.

331
00:21:50,245 --> 00:21:52,545
Gu Nanxi, thank you so much.

332
00:21:53,445 --> 00:21:55,444
This is the first time in my life

333
00:21:55,445 --> 00:21:58,084
to celebrate my birthday with my friends.

334
00:21:58,085 --> 00:22:00,015
I'm very happy tonight.

335
00:22:00,525 --> 00:22:04,564
I feel very lucky
to have all of you as my friends.

336
00:22:04,565 --> 00:22:07,004
Actually, I am not the only one
you should thank.

337
00:22:07,005 --> 00:22:09,865
They all took part in this as well.

338
00:22:11,605 --> 00:22:12,684
That's right.

339
00:22:12,685 --> 00:22:15,764
I have prepared a mystery gift
for all of you.

340
00:22:15,765 --> 00:22:16,884
What mystery gift?

341
00:22:16,885 --> 00:22:17,964
Please tell us!

342
00:22:17,965 --> 00:22:20,884
This mystery gift
can't be opened under the tree.

343
00:22:20,885 --> 00:22:22,085
What is it?

344
00:22:22,765 --> 00:22:25,844
You're annoying.
All this mystery is killing me.

345
00:22:25,845 --> 00:22:28,604
Gu Nanxi, stop beating around the bush.
Tell us now.

346
00:22:28,605 --> 00:22:29,545
All right.

347
00:22:29,845 --> 00:22:32,404
I'm sure all of you are going
to love this gift.

348
00:22:32,405 --> 00:22:34,164
Especially you, Qingqing.

349
00:22:34,165 --> 00:22:35,405
-Really?
-Yes.

350
00:22:35,565 --> 00:22:36,684
Everyone, come with me.

351
00:22:36,685 --> 00:22:38,625
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

352
00:22:44,765 --> 00:22:45,835
We're here.

353
00:22:47,525 --> 00:22:48,644
This is the place?

354
00:22:48,645 --> 00:22:51,284
-Baby, there's nothing here.
-That's right.

355
00:22:51,285 --> 00:22:52,785
Wait for me here.

356
00:22:53,085 --> 00:22:54,044
I'll be back.

357
00:22:54,045 --> 00:22:56,465
Make sure no one leaves, okay?

358
00:22:56,485 --> 00:22:57,615
Wait for me.

359
00:23:00,125 --> 00:23:00,965
Gosh.

360
00:23:01,725 --> 00:23:03,804
I left my bag back there.

361
00:23:03,805 --> 00:23:05,044
I need to go back and get it.

362
00:23:05,045 --> 00:23:06,564
Qingqing, it's dark out there.

363
00:23:06,565 --> 00:23:08,865
-Let me go with you.
-Okay.

364
00:23:08,885 --> 00:23:10,015
Wait for us.

365
00:23:17,645 --> 00:23:18,924
-Hello?
-Yes, Mom?

366
00:23:18,925 --> 00:23:21,044
What? Something went wrong
with the budget?

367
00:23:21,045 --> 00:23:23,364
-I'm coming now.
-Okay, I'm coming home now.

368
00:23:23,365 --> 00:23:27,885
-Sorry, I have to head back.
-Sorry, I have to head back.

369
00:23:32,765 --> 00:23:34,205
It's right here.

370
00:23:46,485 --> 00:23:50,245
CHEN YOUYOU

371
00:24:31,805 --> 00:24:32,645
Qingqing.

372
00:24:48,725 --> 00:24:50,155
Where's everyone?

373
00:25:12,765 --> 00:25:14,125
-Qingqing.
-Yes?

374
00:25:14,125 --> 00:25:17,684
It's almost midnight.
I have a present for you.

375
00:25:17,685 --> 00:25:18,885
It's a song.

376
00:25:19,205 --> 00:25:21,065
It's called "Soulmate."

377
00:25:30,045 --> 00:25:32,685
That day you asked

378
00:25:32,765 --> 00:25:37,525
Are there lights in the dark

379
00:25:37,605 --> 00:25:43,325
I looked up facing the stars

380
00:25:44,445 --> 00:25:50,365
Wondering about the world

381
00:25:50,965 --> 00:25:54,845
Wanting to share everything with you

382
00:25:59,005 --> 00:26:05,925
Brutal wind, damaged sprouts

383
00:26:06,405 --> 00:26:12,445
Spring will lose its meanings

384
00:26:13,165 --> 00:26:16,005
Light breeze

385
00:26:16,085 --> 00:26:19,365
Dreams and scents

386
00:26:19,885 --> 00:26:24,205
Home is where you are

387
00:26:25,565 --> 00:26:31,805
I'm waiting by the stars

388
00:26:32,525 --> 00:26:37,125
The crescent of your eyes

389
00:26:38,605 --> 00:26:45,405
Melody lingering about like the wind

390
00:26:46,765 --> 00:26:52,325
Always by your side

391
00:27:00,285 --> 00:27:01,445
Situ Feng.

392
00:27:02,045 --> 00:27:04,405
Thank you for singing for me.

393
00:27:08,845 --> 00:27:09,725
This song

394
00:27:11,205 --> 00:27:13,445
was my mom's favorite song.

395
00:27:14,125 --> 00:27:15,005
Then...

396
00:27:16,205 --> 00:27:17,335
she fell ill

397
00:27:17,925 --> 00:27:19,295
and passed away.

398
00:27:19,645 --> 00:27:21,045
Situ Feng.

399
00:27:22,965 --> 00:27:24,045
I remember

400
00:27:25,365 --> 00:27:27,175
before my mom left me

401
00:27:27,605 --> 00:27:28,445
she said

402
00:27:30,405 --> 00:27:32,705
if she's not around anymore,

403
00:27:33,005 --> 00:27:36,545
she will turn into a star
to look after me.

404
00:27:38,085 --> 00:27:41,305
I believe your parents would be the same.

405
00:27:42,405 --> 00:27:43,405
Even though

406
00:27:44,405 --> 00:27:45,655
they are gone,

407
00:27:46,405 --> 00:27:47,595
but they have

408
00:27:48,245 --> 00:27:51,365
influenced our lives forever.

409
00:28:04,005 --> 00:28:05,505
Dear Mom and Dad.

410
00:28:07,685 --> 00:28:09,045
Are you both

411
00:28:11,965 --> 00:28:13,645
doing well up there?

412
00:28:20,685 --> 00:28:23,245
When I was little,

413
00:28:23,325 --> 00:28:25,564
my mom gave me this guitar pick.

414
00:28:25,565 --> 00:28:29,964
I turned it into a necklace,
hoping it'd bring me good luck.

415
00:28:29,965 --> 00:28:32,215
Now, I'm giving it to you.

416
00:28:32,245 --> 00:28:35,084
I hope it will bring you good luck too.

417
00:28:35,085 --> 00:28:36,025
Situ Feng.

418
00:28:36,645 --> 00:28:38,524
This is such a precious item to you.

419
00:28:38,525 --> 00:28:40,764
Are you sure you want to give it to me?

420
00:28:40,765 --> 00:28:43,324
Why? Do you think I'm a petty person?

421
00:28:43,325 --> 00:28:46,365
That song was not the only gift, okay?

422
00:28:48,285 --> 00:28:49,295
Try it on.

423
00:28:58,885 --> 00:29:00,625
Thank you, Situ Feng.

424
00:29:00,965 --> 00:29:03,575
I promise to cherish it for you.

425
00:29:25,965 --> 00:29:28,644
To think I actually prepared
fireworks for them

426
00:29:28,645 --> 00:29:33,465
and they left me hanging,
to be all romantic with one another.

427
00:29:35,845 --> 00:29:38,964
Why do I always end up
helping other people?

428
00:29:38,965 --> 00:29:42,995
I am not going to set off the fireworks
this time.

429
00:29:43,605 --> 00:29:46,245
Situ Feng, look at the fireworks.

430
00:29:46,605 --> 00:29:48,564
It's rare to have fireworks at this hour.

431
00:29:48,565 --> 00:29:50,675
Who set off the fireworks?

432
00:29:50,725 --> 00:29:52,035
It's beautiful.

433
00:29:52,845 --> 00:29:54,005
Perhaps

434
00:29:54,565 --> 00:29:58,515
it was your necklace
that brought us the fireworks.

435
00:30:09,685 --> 00:30:10,925
Chen Qingqing!

436
00:30:11,005 --> 00:30:12,924
Stay away from Situ Feng from now on.

437
00:30:12,925 --> 00:30:14,684
Isn't this Situ Feng's necklace?

438
00:30:14,685 --> 00:30:16,375
Why is it with you?

439
00:30:16,525 --> 00:30:18,645
-Qingqing.
-Lin Yiyang!

440
00:30:18,725 --> 00:30:23,315
Didn't I tell you?
Don't lay your hands on Chen Qingqing.

441
00:30:25,725 --> 00:30:27,035
This is helium.

442
00:30:27,045 --> 00:30:31,245
It will create a magical effect
when people inhale it.

443
00:30:32,645 --> 00:30:33,525
Fangfang!

444
00:30:33,605 --> 00:30:37,284
Qingqing, we need to find Situ Feng
as soon as possible.

445
00:30:37,285 --> 00:30:40,505
This isn't the first time he disappeared.

446
